Su.9 — Khuddakachatushpada

atha khalu chatvaraḥ pādāḥ — bhiṣak, dravyam, upasthātā, rogī iti;
tatra bhiṣajaḥ śrutaṃ paryavadātam bahuśo dṛṣṭakarmāṇaṃ dakṣaṃ śucim iti guṇāḥ;
dravyasya bahutvam, akalpatāṃ (akalpanāyogyatāṃ), anekavidhakalpayogyatāṃ, sampat iti guṇāḥ;
upasthātuḥ jñānaṃ, dakṣatā, anurāgaḥ, śaucam iti guṇāḥ;
rogino dhṛtiḥ, smṛtiḥ, abhirūpatā, ājñāpāyitvaṃ iti guṇāḥ.
